title: Holes and a series of rabbits
description: Holes and a series of rabbits is a debut poetry collection that takes you on a journey through a whimsical lens, exploring life through relatable themes of love, nature, and ultimately self-discovery. Elizabeth Helmich's poems are often introspective, at times humorous, and offer a silver lining to navigate the holes of life. Come, follow the rabbit.
author: Elizabeth Helmich
